pageContext.claim: “You probably read about the young people in Peru and young people in Brazil, and they were absolutely stuck, and we got them out. Got them -- almost everybody is out now, back home with their parents, their wives, their husbands.”
pageContext.analysis: By many accounts, the State Department's efforts to bring Americans back to the country were faltering. Trump highlighted two countries, but the problem was acute elsewhere. "But in Nepal, hundreds are still stuck," The New York Times reported.
